00:39:19.151 --> 00:39:20.753
Ngunit hindi iyon madali.

00:39:21.487 --> 00:39:24.523
Ang pagiging masayahin at tiwala,
ngunit maalalahanin din.

00:39:27.092 --> 00:39:28.360
May asawa na ba siya ngayon?

00:39:29.161 --> 00:39:30.763
